      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend the Foreign Assistance Act of 1961 to require information on the status of excessive surveillance and use of advanced technology to violate privacy and other fundamental human rights be included in the annual Country Reports on Human Rights Practices.</title>
      </item>
